" Personal Mappings

nnoremap <leader>t :! tree\|less <cr>
nnoremap <leader>w :w<cr>
nnoremap <leader>W zz
nnoremap <leader>q :q<cr>
nnoremap <leader><leader> <c-^>

" map escape key to ;; 
inoremap ;; <ESC>
inoremap jk <ESC>
inoremap kj <ESC>

" Lines length up to 80 characters


autocmd FileType haskell highlight OverLength ctermbg=darkred ctermfg=white guibg=#FFD9D9 | match OverLength /\%81v.\+/
